    Goal interface to implement the composite pattern

    Subject interface for the observer pattern

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bomb
    A bomb entity that is able to be picked up and dropped/activated.
    Boulder
    A boulder in the dungeon that can be moved by the player.
    CompositeGoal
    A class for composite goal that implements the Goal interface.
    Door  
    Dungeon
    A dungeon in the interactive dungeon player.
    DungeonApplication  
    DungeonController
    A JavaFX controller for the dungeon.
    DungeonControllerLoader
    A DungeonLoader that also creates the necessary ImageViews for the UI, connects them via listeners to the model, and creates a controller.
    DungeonLoader
    Loads a dungeon from a .json file.
    Enemy
    An enemy in the dungeon that wanders around or chases the player if it finds him.
    EnemyGoal
    A simple Enemy Goal that tracks whether the player has killed all the enemies in the dungeon
    Entity
    An entity in the dungeon.
    Exit
    An exit in the dungeon
    ExitGoal
    An exit goal for the dungeon game
    GameState
    Tracks the game state of the dungeon game The game is completed when the player wins or loses the game The game state tracks all the goals of the game
    InvinciblePotion
    An invincible potion in the dungeon game Player gains invincibility when player drink the potion
    Key  
    Lit  
    Node  
    NoWeapon
    A weapon strategy stating the player has no weapon.
    Player
    The player entity
    Spawned  
    Switch
    A switch in the dungeon that can be activated to by pushing a boulder on it.
    SwitchGoal
    A switch goal that tracks the number of switches activated The goal is completed when number of activated switches equal total switches
    Sword
    A sword in the dungeon.
    SwordAttack
    A weapon strategy stating the player has a Sword.
    Treasure
    A treasure that can be picked up by the player in the dungeon
    TreasureGoal
    A treasure goal that tracks the number of treasure collected by the player
    Unlit  
    Wall
    A wall that blocks the movement of all other entities in the dungeon
